00:36:46,660 --> 00:36:48,140
Close to nature,

573
00:36:48,390 --> 00:36:49,390
and get some exercise.

574
00:36:49,390 --> 00:36:50,620
What's not to love?

575
00:36:52,340 --> 00:36:53,180
Besides,

576
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:55,910
eating, singing,
and going to the movies?

577
00:36:56,044 --> 00:36:57,444
Doing all that feels like an affair.

578
00:36:57,780 --> 00:36:59,110
But a walk in the park?

579
00:36:59,620 --> 00:37:01,110
Platonic. Pure.

580
00:37:03,140 --> 00:37:04,300
Almost romantic.

581
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:08,260
People always try
to fill what they lack.

582
00:37:13,430 --> 00:37:14,470
You're killing me.

583
00:37:15,340 --> 00:37:16,430
I need to take this call.

584
00:37:16,910 --> 00:37:17,510
Go ahead.

585
00:37:19,220 --> 00:37:19,740
Yes?

586
00:37:22,140 --> 00:37:24,470
Nothing can go wrong
with our final roadshow.

587
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:26,870
Also,

588
00:37:26,870 --> 00:37:28,620
that wine from last time?

589
00:37:28,620 --> 00:37:29,510
Not good enough.

590
00:37:29,780 --> 00:37:30,390
Change it.

591
00:37:31,910 --> 00:37:32,910
Okay.

592
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,030
Got it.

593
00:37:34,910 --> 00:37:35,470
See you.

594
00:37:36,660 --> 00:37:37,700
You really are hands-on.

595
00:37:39,870 --> 00:37:41,220
I can handle it.

596
00:37:41,220 --> 00:37:42,260
Silly guy.

597
00:37:52,590 --> 00:37:53,390
Qingcheng,

598
00:37:54,390 --> 00:37:55,470
how about...

599
00:38:00,180 --> 00:38:01,430
How about we give it a try?

600
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:03,220
Where do you get this confidence?

601
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:06,340
Come on.

602
00:38:06,660 --> 00:38:08,950
We are clearly the youngest people
in this park.

603
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:09,620
Right?

604
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:11,555
You even came all the way here with me.

605
00:38:11,555 --> 00:38:14,180
That's a kid right there.
And a group of elementary schoolers.

606
00:38:14,180 --> 00:38:15,030
Do you not see them?

607
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:16,950
I'm not joking.

608
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:18,140
I'm serious.

609
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:20,180
Give us a chance.

610
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:33,910
Qingcheng,

611
00:38:34,950 --> 00:38:36,340
I know what you're worried about.

612
00:38:37,111 --> 00:38:38,390
I've already set aside a huge sum

613
00:38:38,430 --> 00:38:39,620
for my wife and son.

614
00:38:40,470 --> 00:38:41,590
Whether we divorce or not,

615
00:38:41,590 --> 00:38:42,660
that money is theirs.

616
00:38:43,430 --> 00:38:44,070
Of course,

617
00:38:44,430 --> 00:38:45,550
I know no amount of money

618
00:38:45,550 --> 00:38:47,300
can make up for the youth she gave up.

619
00:38:47,660 --> 00:38:48,820
But this is...

620
00:38:52,070 --> 00:38:53,660
This is me buying back my own freedom.

621
00:38:53,910 --> 00:38:55,340
I'm objectifying myself.

622
00:38:56,660 --> 00:38:58,140
That makes it fair, right?

623
00:39:05,950 --> 00:39:06,820
Zhong Qingcheng.

624
00:39:07,660 --> 00:39:10,220
I really, really want to be with you.

625
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:11,070
I mean it.

626
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:12,590
So...

627
00:39:12,870 --> 00:39:13,950
We get together,

628
00:39:14,140 --> 00:39:14,820
then what?

629
00:39:14,820 --> 00:39:15,470
Then...

630
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:17,300
Then,

631
00:39:18,620 --> 00:39:20,300
we live happily ever after.

632
00:39:38,300 --> 00:39:40,180
The most exciting countdown moment.

633
00:39:40,510 --> 00:39:44,990
Ten, nine, eight, seven, six,

634
00:39:44,990 --> 00:39:50,300
five, four, three, two, one.

635
00:39:50,545 --> 00:39:53,312
(HKEX, Shishi Technology)

636
00:40:06,264 --> 00:40:07,960
(Congratulations
to Yancheng Shishi Technology)

637
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,600
(on its successful listing
in Hong Kong, China)

638
00:40:38,289 --> 00:40:44,400
(12 Hours Ago)

639
00:41:39,510 --> 00:41:40,340
What's on your mind?

640
00:41:44,430 --> 00:41:45,510
I was thinking

641
00:41:46,590 --> 00:41:48,180
about the first time I came to Shanghai

642
00:41:49,510 --> 00:41:50,590
when I got into college.

643
00:41:52,030 --> 00:41:53,140
I stayed in a tiny hotel

644
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:54,300
near the school.

645
00:41:55,510 --> 00:41:57,390
It was 80 yuan a night.

646
00:41:59,340 --> 00:42:00,590
When I took a shower,

647
00:42:00,950 --> 00:42:03,870
the water ran down the steps

648
00:42:04,300 --> 00:42:06,070
and soaked the floor.

649
00:42:08,066 --> 00:42:10,990
I was too scared to call the front desk.
I was afraid they'd scold me.

650
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,910
So, I grabbed a rag

651
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:18,220
and mopped it all up myself.

652
00:42:19,780 --> 00:42:20,550
Honey.

653
00:42:22,266 --> 00:42:23,377
I never imagined

654
00:42:23,377 --> 00:42:25,220
that some broke kid like me
would end up here.

655
00:42:25,550 --> 00:42:26,180
Seriously.

656
00:42:29,430 --> 00:42:30,510
When I was a boy,

657
00:42:31,110 --> 00:42:32,660
I played marbles.

658
00:42:32,910 --> 00:42:34,110
And my son?

659
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:36,140
He plays golf.

660
00:42:39,820 --> 00:42:41,260
When I think of it like that,

661
00:42:42,510 --> 00:42:44,740
everything I've been through
was worth it.

662
00:42:47,700 --> 00:42:50,110
Tomorrow's the big day.

663
00:42:50,470 --> 00:42:53,110
Don't go down memory lane tonight.

664
00:42:54,044 --> 00:42:55,111
Think about something else.

665
00:42:59,030 --> 00:42:59,990
Something else?

666
00:43:02,390 --> 00:43:03,220
Honey.

667
00:43:08,340 --> 00:43:10,180
Did you

668
00:43:12,430 --> 00:43:15,590
prepare something special for me?

669
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:20,110
Take a guess.

670
00:43:37,340 --> 00:43:38,300
Open it.

671
00:43:44,950 --> 00:43:46,470
I wonder what it is?

672
00:44:06,050 --> 00:44:06,866
(All Photos)

673
00:44:06,888 --> 00:44:09,520
(Congratulations on its
successful listing in Hong Kong, China.)

674
00:44:09,520 --> 00:44:10,413
(Moments)

675
00:44:10,415 --> 00:44:12,280
(Keep moving forward,
and the future is bright.)

676
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:14,460
