Mr. Yang: Impressive.)

679
00:44:17,270 --> 00:44:19,495
(Mr. Li: Count on you.
Dr. Fan: Congrats.)

680
00:44:19,510 --> 00:44:21,910
(Mr. Zhang: Congrats.
Mr. Yang: Finally made it.)

681
00:44:21,910 --> 00:44:24,910
(Liu Ye: Respect.
Mr. Hao: You're a role model.)

682
00:44:24,911 --> 00:44:26,880
