Mr. Chen: Congrats.)

683
00:44:39,660 --> 00:44:43,190
♪I always thought♪

684
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:49,810
♪Life stayed calm like a quiet lake♪

685
00:44:51,610 --> 00:44:56,940
♪But just one breeze♪

686
00:44:57,720 --> 00:45:01,180
♪Could dry it up like a hollow pit♪

687
00:45:03,680 --> 00:45:06,680
♪Gains and losses blur together♪

688
00:45:09,610 --> 00:45:13,040
♪Goodbyes are when we look our best♪

689
00:45:15,650 --> 00:45:19,680
♪You need to face yourself♪

690
00:45:21,990 --> 00:45:25,080
♪To rebuild or to tear it all down♪

691
00:45:25,640 --> 00:45:31,090
♪I clearly saw the moonlight♪

692
00:45:31,830 --> 00:45:36,960
♪Lighting up the entrance all around♪

693
00:45:37,810 --> 00:45:43,280
♪The world is one big theatre♪

694
00:45:44,090 --> 00:45:49,170
♪Where people come and go♪

695
00:45:49,740 --> 00:45:55,060
♪One day, I'll learn♪

696
00:45:55,770 --> 00:46:00,850
♪It doesn't matter
if you're the protagonist or not♪

697
00:46:01,620 --> 00:46:07,240
♪Life will still reach its end♪

698
00:46:08,120 --> 00:46:13,460
♪Whether you're worthy or not♪

699
00:46:13,840 --> 00:46:19,330
♪I'm grateful for every day♪

700
00:46:19,770 --> 00:46:25,020
♪I spend being someone I can be proud of♪

701
00:46:25,740 --> 00:46:31,690
♪Walking through life from start to end♪

702
00:46:32,560 --> 00:46:37,080
♪Whether I'm loud or quiet♪

703
00:46:38,180 --> 00:46:41,500
♪It's still me♪
